Package controller

Class ChooseMidiDevice

java.lang.Object
controller.ChooseMidiDevice
public class ChooseMidiDevice
extends java.lang.Object
Controller controls the choose midi device, and other options screen. Manages the options, and when the user navigates to the game area, the config object and midi device object will be passed to it
